			<div class="text-white">
				<h2 class="text-center mb-12 md:!ml-0 md:!w-[400px] md:!text-left lg:!w-[600px]">Мобильное приложение Jetour Connect</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 mb-12">
